# proto toolchain pins for invoice-extractor — https://moonrepo.dev/proto
# Run `proto install` (no args) from the repo root to install everything below.
#
# go: matches go/go.mod exactly. The official ollama/ollama/api client forces
#     go 1.26 (the documented "Go forkability tax"); keep these in lockstep.
# python: project standard is 3.12. This provides the interpreter; create the
#     app venv from it, e.g.  python -m venv python/.venv
go = "1.26.0"
python = "~3.12"
